      "body": "- Replace recursive syntax with syntax similar to RFC9539\r\n- Change CA-specific option prefix from \"-<ca_name>-\" to \"ca-<ca_name>-\" to conform to new syntax\r\n- Add proposal on how to defeat active adversaries using SVCB DNS records (address the issues raised in Appendix B of RFC9539",
